high_descs: Turn around and go face the table in between the table and the refrigerator.
Pick up the gray knife in front of the apple on the table.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Place the knife in the black mug in the sink.
Pick up the mug with knife in it.
Turn around and go to the green table.
Place the mug with knife in it on the right side of the fork on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put the mug with knife in it on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the side of the kitchen island by the fridge.
Pick up the butter knife on the table.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Place the knife in the mug.
Pick up the mug.
Turn around and face the island again.
Put the mug back on the kitchen island to the right of the fork.
anns.task_desc: Place a mug with a knife in it on the kitchen island.

high_descs: Turn around, walk into the kitchen, and approach the green table
Pick up the butter knife closest to table's edge
Turn around and walk up to the kitchen sink
Put the knife into the mug that's in the sink
Pick up the mug from the sink
Turn around and walk back to the table
Place the mug down on the table
anns.task_desc: Place a mug with knife onto the table

high_descs: turn right and go towards the stove, turn left at the green table, at the center of the table turn left to face it
pick up the knife that is to the left of the yellow pencil
turn around and move to the sink
put the knife into the coffee mug that is in the sink
pick up the coffee mug with the knife inside it
turn back around and move back to the green table
place the cup with the knife inside on to the green table to the right of the fork
anns.task_desc: place a knife that is in a coffee mug onto the green table

high_descs: Turn to your right, forward a little then turn right, then turn left walk forward then face the table on your left
Pick up the knife on the table
Turn around on your left and face the sink
Put the knife in the mug which is on the sink
Pick up the mug with knife on the sink
Turn to your left then face the table
Put the mug with knife on the table
anns.task_desc: Put the mug with knife on the table

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the green table to your right.
Grab the butter knife on the table.
Carrying the butter knife, walk to the sink to your left.
Place the butter knife into the cup in the sink.
Pick up the cup with the butter knife in it.
Carrying the cup with the butter knife in it, turn to the table behind you.
Place the cup with the butter knife in it on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a cup with a butter knife in it on the table.
